\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]...So, how about it? Did you like the room?
\n<Minato>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Well, um... I guess so.

\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]I give a vague answer that can be interpreted
either way. Even though I think it's childish of
me, I can't help but find it annoying to play
along with this man named Udo.

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]The food is pretty good, right? I prepared the best
for this day, you know~♪
\n<Minato>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Well... it's delicious...
\n<Sonoda>\FF[61]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]So... Director Udo, could you tell us soon?

\FF[61]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Sonoda-san urged Director Udo to speak. Perhaps they sensed
something from my response and were considerate of
me.
\n<Udo>\FF[61]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Tch... Premature ejaculators don't get any girls, huh?

\n<Udo>\FF[61]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Hmph, well... fine. Then let's start with the matter of
this mansion.
\FF[61]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]And finally... Udo began to talk about work.

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]...Well, that's about it. Minato-chan, do you have any
questions?
\n<Minato>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Um, well...

\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]I once... organized the information I received from
Director Udo in my head. Among that information,
there were surprising facts.

\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]First of all, it seems that this mansion was inherited
as a legacy from Director Udo's grandfather. And
that grandfather is none other than the world-
famous director, Isamu Udo, who is said to be a
great director of the Showa era. I was surprised
by this fact.

\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Some of the works he left behind are well-known even
to someone like me who is completely ignorant
about movies. It seems that the film Director Udo
Takeru is making this time is an homage to one of
those works.
\n<Minato>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Regarding the character I will be playing...

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Ah... You must have been surprised, right? The moment I
saw you, Minato-chan, on the TV station, I felt
something like a fateful connection.

\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Since the script arrived, I have read it over and over
again. The character I will be playing, 'Reiko,'
is incredibly similar to me in terms of
appearance, personality, and even the way she
speaks... except for one thing.

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]So, Minato-chan, I want you to strive to get as close
as possible to the character named 'Reiko' during
this training camp.

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]To start off... let's stop using that way of
speaking from now on. It's not that we're being
informal, but it's part of getting into character,
you know?
\n<Minato>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Yes... No... Ah, I understand.

\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]I'm actually confused about being forced to speak
naturally for the role. But... I felt hesitant
about acting childish, so I managed to put on a
fake smile and respond somehow.

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]If there's anything you don't understand, feel free
to rely on me, okay? After all, I'm here as both
your acting coach and director, you know?
\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Well then...
!$宇堂
!$宇堂
!$音々(ライダースーツ)
!$音々(ライダースーツ)
!$マネージャー
!$マネージャー

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Today, I'll let you rest first, okay~? Minato-chan, you
shouldn't stay up late, okay?

\n<Minato>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Good work. I'm a complete amateur when it comes to
acting, but please take care of me starting from
tomorrow.

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Ah, let's do our best together, okay~? Oh... just to
make sure, the lesson starts at 1 PM, okay~?

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Starting the day after tomorrow, the lessons will begin
from the moment you leave your room at 1 PM, so
make sure to be in your room by that time, okay?

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Oh, and as for meals, feel free to use the
ingredients here however you like. Until 1 PM, you
have free time, so make sure to have your meal
before then.
\n<Minato>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Yes, I understand.
\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Well then, good work~
\n<Sonoda>\FF[61]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Good work! Please take care of our Minato!

\.\SE[タイプライタ]Ｐ\.\SE[タイプライタ]Ｍ \.\SE[タイプライタ]８\.\SE[タイプライタ]：\.\SE[タイプライタ]０\.\S
E[タイプライタ]０

\n<Sonoda>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF]How is it? Do you think you can manage? From what
I've heard, it seems like there isn't much I can
help with...

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F]Hehe, please don't spoil me too much. When I truly feel
like I can't handle it anymore, I'll speak up
myself.

\n<Sonoda>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF]I see... You do have some clumsy aspects aside from
being involved in music, don't you?
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F]I'm not a klutz! What are you saying, seriously...

\n<Sonoda>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF]Hahaha... Well then, shall we go back to our rooms? It's a
bit early to sleep, but it's better to rest early
today to prepare for tomorrow.

\n<Sonoda>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF]Come on, let's go. You can't go back alone in this
dark, right?

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F](Does Sonoda really think of me as a child who can't go
to the bathroom alone at night? What does he
really think of me...)
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F]\}(Well... I'll go back with you though...)
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F]Ah... Sonoda-san...
\n<Sonoda>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF]Good morning, Minato... Hm? What's wrong?

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F](Ugh... I feel such an indescribable sense of guilt... I
can't... I can't look him in the eye...)

\n<Sonoda>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF]Ah, is this it? Minato, do you want to drink too?
There are mugs in that shelf over there.
A
\n<Sonoda>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF]Huh...? The mug is on that shelf over there, \C[0].
